<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="neglect-vt">neglect <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /nɪ'ɡlekt/    美 /nɪ'ɡlekt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>忽视；疏忽；漏做 (某事)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>neglect one’s duty 
玩忽职守</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When an opportunity is neglected, it never comes back to you. 
机不可失，时不再来。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I <strong>neglected to</strong> lock the door. 
我忘了锁门。</p></div></div>